               stealing, on the <rs id="t18201206-81-cd505" type="crimeDate">4th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18201206-81-off504 t18201206-81-cd505"></join>, one watch, value 2 l.; one ribbon, value 1 d.; one key, value 1 d.; one coat, value 30 s.; one waistcoat, value 5 s. and one handkerchief, value 6 d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18201206-81-victim821" type="victimName">
